attributionInfo.brokerName: Better Homes and Gardens Real Estate Welcome Home

data.description: BUTTE COUNTY~BEAUTIFUL LAKE OROVILLE~ Just 5 minutes away.  Unique ~Contemporary~ Octagon Shaped~ Home.  With a little added addition for some extra space.  Built in 1976.  Very Unique 1425 sq. ft. 2/2.  Very clean and has been well kept.  Nice wood floors and unique interior.  Nice pull down blinds throughout the home. Located on .21 of an acre located in the Kelly Ridge Subdivision, Oroville Ca. If you are interested in FISHING, BOATING, SKIING, SIGHT SEEING.  THIS IS THE PLACE FOR YOU. Central Heat and Air with a Beautiful Stone Fireplace for those cozy nights.  Great Deck, Single car garage, Storage and PARKING FOR YOUR BOAT..  Marina is just minutes from the house. Gravel drive and Beautiful Mature,  easy to care for landscape in front of the home. Sits back off of the street a bit for a little privacy! Property is partially chain linked fenced Both sides and the back.  Small chain link little yard. Some automatic watering in place.  Some unique rock and landscape work here.  Take a look !!!  Sellers are very motivated.  Buyers to verify all information to their satisfaction.
